{"tid":1788761,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"［半即時］聖誕前一條毒撚遊東京7日","createTime":"2019-12-19T02:47:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-28T08:25:41.000Z","uid":43081,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"8d25fdc65a60bcd7ad31d20022391b94b3e586dd","tid":1788761,"uid":43081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T02:47:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ju7JY3w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJu7JY3w.jpg&h=c19501d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n前晚坐凌晨機飛羽田<br />\n竟然冇delay 準時4點幾去到羽田<br />\n仲要打手指模同拎行李都0阻滯<br />\n5點左右已經完成所有野<br />\n<br />\n濕9酒店reception 8點先開工，豐州水曜日又冇開<br />\n所以變去築地食早餐先<br />\n飛機訓唔到，又凍，唔想食生冷野<br />\n所以主力食熱野<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bZy5sY7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbZy5sY7.jpg&h=a78161e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iHJUmi9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiHJUmi9.jpg&h=0d5d58e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ggfjxqQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FggfjxqQ.jpg&h=21f0abc1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F1Q7Gjc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF1Q7Gjc.jpg&h=7beac472&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QQAb7Ze.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQQAb7Ze.jpg&h=6d8058d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FK0jxqW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFK0jxqW.jpg&h=4d76360a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n之前一直想試下檔牛雜飯，係幾好食，味好濃，又煮得夠淋<br />\n海膽饅熱熱地，舊海膽半熟半溶咁好正<br />\n扑多左隻海膽食,2000円、隻海膽好鮮但其實唔多值<br />\n<br />\n之後去左千駄木間酒店掉低喼直接步行去上野動物園（今日原行程想去老秋睇akb公演，但可惜抽唔中，冇行程plan) <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qF4cStX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqF4cStX.jpg&h=9800123e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VjmKJAE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVjmKJAE.jpg&h=dc433762&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FtN6ct1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFtN6ct1.jpg&h=51fd8575&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rW4oY83.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrW4oY83.jpg&h=25ef064a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n堆爬蟲類好可愛<br />\n<br />\n行左兩個幾鐘 之後直接步行去老秋<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0EzHvgk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0EzHvgk.jpg&h=b2e8e6b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Euohi9H.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEuohi9H.jpg&h=d2b6e6bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kutdBWp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkutdBWp.jpg&h=d6edfa08&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n食垃圾gundam cafe同akb cafe, akb theatre 那邊有event入唔到，所以第一次坐出面<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mB6R73W.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmB6R73W.jpg&h=aafe07c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nMetal build rx93好撚型<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ziWKJCu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FziWKJCu.jpg&h=d33d17c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n屌多左碗拉麵就去汐留睇燈飾<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BVzTBXT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBVzTBXT.jpg&h=d8b561d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/unow74A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Funow74A.jpg&h=5e7dc1fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UXCJZbi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUXCJZbi.jpg&h=c582d56c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/y1YdBX1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy1YdBX1.jpg&h=90152e40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SwgR74J.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSwgR74J.jpg&h=f4e4179a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n係幾靚 又多女 但一條毒撚去好似唔多適合<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fb16467e8900bd7c51243fac4045e40666e2d92","tid":1788761,"uid":43081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T02:47:36.000Z","msg":"而家去緊姆明公園"},{"pid":"5a4157cf4dc8747c1d9d3089ddb77f0b43f8cb8a","tid":1788761,"uid":122134,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T02:48:35.000Z","msg":"士多啤利有密集恐懼"},{"pid":"94d532721849ed4199878663b78abb0fc4598b9f","tid":1788761,"uid":43081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5a4157cf4dc8747c1d9d3089ddb77f0b43f8cb8a","tid":1788761,"uid":122134,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T02:48:35.000Z","msg":"士多啤利有密集恐懼"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T02:57:28.000Z","msg":"我想搵大淡雪 但唔見<br />\n9買杯細既食左算"},{"pid":"e127d079d710e7f1e3f457db49aa70e42891ad90","tid":1788761,"uid":42367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T03:45:53.000Z","msg":"lm 22我都出發東京"},{"pid":"54f0be559ad1112785c3a74feb51d9f64254828e","tid":1788761,"uid":31051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T03:54:50.000Z","msg":"留名26出發<br />\n去コミケ<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ee884b24d70599d4a0180e3e622aa28e4f64cd7","tid":1788761,"uid":96406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T03:58:33.000Z","msg":"會唔會去harajuku?"},{"pid":"3ae70d3f49af616dd0190cd0cfdc847161fa802f","tid":1788761,"uid":43081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"54f0be559ad1112785c3a74feb51d9f64254828e","tid":1788761,"uid":31051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T03:54:50.000Z","msg":"留名26出發<br />\n去コミケ<img src=