/>\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fhKwpgm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfhKwpgm.jpg&h=661cf165&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n姆明公園<br />\n有紅葉既應該會靚好多<br />\n個姆明谷模型有4季變化<br />\n好治癒"},{"pid":"dec0343a1027f2cac6771c054ccfb3799a0c09cb","tid":1788761,"uid":43081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T05:08:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/W5Yk2cr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FW5Yk2cr.jpg&h=389483d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7csenct.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7csenct.jpg&h=d811938a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fXZDOSv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfXZDOSv.jpg&h=8ca4f5d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cAi9a5R.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcAi9a5R.jpg&h=6e456b6c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ef925b91c79132f6f0e1aaa10d8e9b03f1ba091f","tid":1788761,"uid":55851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T05:13:06.000Z","msg":"見唔見到有催情朱古力賣?"},{"pid":"3ceb883794c06912897d84bfcf5ef4d642a871e0","tid":1788761,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T05:13:59.000Z","msg":"去東京唔坐skyliner=白去"},{"pid":"d70349394f5a8cbf782a685befb34ed57dbc06f2","tid":1788761,"uid":43081,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T06:39:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EaKsHHo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEaKsHHo.jpg&h=841c5dcf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有手足寫左光復香港時代革命<br />\n我補多句五大訴求缺一不可"},{"pid":"7e72baac14a75e9bd628958fb97c900958de28df","tid":1788761,"uid":60209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T11:42:30.000Z","msg":"好貼留名跟進<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee4b6b2ad940fac2625ccb33a9b688dd5d7779d4","tid":1788761,"uid":43081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T17:10:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ha94Oqq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHa94Oqq.jpg&h=0d9b707a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n排左45分鐘食左碗無敵家<br />\n第一次食<br />\n肉多湯濃面正<br />\n蛋 餃子普通<br />\n係好食<br />\n但如果第一次去東京想玩多d地方既人唔建議去排<br />\n或者排黎當宵夜食完返酒店訓"},{"pid":"c2535d9d516bff46bfd5db405b69290cc00e7c67","tid":1788761,"uid":43081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T17:15:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YaUXo0F.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYaUXo0F.jpg&h=880cc6e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n去tower record買左呢堆<br />\n買cd player原因係有個玩開貴膽機既舊同事教我cd player仲好聲過兩三萬既磚 所以買部玩下<br />\n<br />\n感覺好似好過我部hiby r6<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e09e328b31423087a61eb738d26bc27910233ca","tid":1788761,"uid":43081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T17:21:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UjPcXmV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUjPcXmV.jpg&h=a3515d6b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n夾左4000円左右<br />\n基本上成功用個勾打正個圈條邊兩三下就會成功擊落，不過我成日拎太盡中空氣<br />\n<br />\n個仆街店員見我3下就中隻悟空，換走左我夾慣既那一邊（1部機左右各放一隻，佢見我慣左右邊，所以右邊冇補貨焗我夾左邊），即刻走"},{"pid":"de73f54c3f5ecb404c4149a47163c0feedd06a3b","tid":1788761,"uid":43081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T17:24:20.000Z","msg":"姆明公園手信，派完俾同事我可留起個罐<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wKSVaKn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwKSVaKn.jpg&h=fc355cd3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"831f80ad2fddab1129dbe16be6324a0e1ee61f19","tid":1788761,"uid":43081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T17:25:46.000Z","msg":"聽朝去下豐洲望下有乜排<br />\n下午未諗好做乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b